div.div:
Tauri does not support SSR based frameworks due to the fact that they, like the name suggests, require a locally running server and make no sense to use in an installed application
Most frameworks however support SSG/SPA, so even if your chosen framework uses SSR by default it's fairly likely it also supports SSG/SPA one way or another
